import React, { useEffect } from 'react'; import { BrowserRouter, Route } from 'react-router-dom'; import { useHistory } from "react-router-dom"; const Routines = (props) => { const routines = props.routines; const setRoutines = props.setRoutines; return <>

Routines

{routines.map((routine, idx) =>

{routine.name}

Goal:

{routine.goal}

Activities:

{routine.activities.map((activity) => <>

Name:

{activity.name}

Description:

{activity.description}

Duration:

{activity.duration}

{activity.count}

)}

Creator:

{routine.creatorName}

)}
} export default Routines;
